WEBVTT

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:31.080
uchun hajviy ko’rsatuvga
aylantirganini tushungandir.

00:01:31.800 --> 00:01:33.056
Biroq bu kulgili emasdi.

00:01:33.080 --> 00:01:35.416
Televizorda odamlar ustidan
hazil qilishsa,

00:01:35.440 --> 00:01:36.656
miriqib kulardingiz.

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:38.538
Bu kun haqida biror kulgili narsani

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:42.336
eslolmayman.
Bu mening bir ko’rinishim edi

00:01:42.360 --> 00:01:45.856
va bu vaziyatga, omma oldida
rad etilishga qayta duch kelmaslik uchun

00:01:45.880 --> 00:01:47.760
o’limga ham tayyor edim.

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:49.896
Bu bir ko’rinishim.

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:52.376
Shiddatli sakkiz yildan so’ng,

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:54.376
shaxrimizga—Beijing, Xitoyga Bill Geyts

00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:55.616
nutq so’zlash uchun

00:01:55.640 --> 00:01:56.856
tashrif buyurdi

00:01:56.880 --> 00:01:58.616
va men uning nutqini eshitdim.

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:00.936
Bu kishi menga yoqib qoldi.